{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stood [? on ?] [? appel. ?] That, that's, that was-- took up most of the day, standing [? at ?] [? appel. ?] Standing in roll call, at roll call, in lines of 5 or 10.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stood there for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't, we didn't work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- I never got hit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never got hit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I vegetated, to tell you the truth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What I remember about Bergen-Belsen, and I think that this can't rest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At least, it gives me an idea what conditions were like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was so impressed with a group of women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were French women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were, they said they were the wives French officers who came into the camp after we had been there already a while.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were so animated and so full of life to me that I would just sit there and watch them, because they looked so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they put on makeup in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they sang songs, French songs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as a child, I thought there was something special about the French people, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I remember these, these French women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I went back to the Bergen-Belsen memorial site in 1991, I spoke to the director of that camp, Dr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thomas Raha.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told him about these French women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another woman, Renata la Coeur, wrote a journal in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She mentioned these French women, and that, in order to show their resistance and their rebellion to the Germans, they would dress in red, white, and blue colors, the colors of the French flag.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but they were so fabulous to me because the other people there looked like-- I didn't know if they were living or dead.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
